data.description: RARE TO FIND!! NO HOA**NO Mello-Roose**LOW PROPERTY TAXES** SINGLE FAMILY** BIG LOT** 6 BEDROOMS + LOFT **HIGH CEILING***   2 BEDROOMS DOWNSTAIRS** 4 BEDROOMS UPSTAIRS** 3 FULL BATHROOMS** POOL-SIZE LOT** WOOD FLOORING** UPDATED KITCHEN** GREAT FOR BIG FAMILIES OR TURNING ONE ROOM DOWNSTAIRS INTO A RENTAL OR OFFICE SPACE!**This WOW-worthy home, boasting 6 bedrooms, 3 full bathrooms, and a loft with vaulted ceilings, is a true gem located in a desirable neighborhood, less than 10 minutes' drive to the beautiful lake of Lake Elsinore. With 2 bedrooms downstairs and a huge front yard that can easily be turned into a huge parking space. updated home features wood flooring, updated kitchen and countertop, as well as a sprawling pool-sized lot. This home is designed to exceed your expectations, and the best part is that there is NO HOA. Prepare yourself to be amazed by this exceptional property that defines the pinnacle of comfort and exclusivity, whether you have guests in town or in-laws staying in, if you have a big family that need more space or you work from home so you can make use of an office room and a gym room, the possibilities are endless, and the sky is the limit. Schedule a tour today. THIS HOME IS A TRUE GEM!
